           INITIALIZE    WK-AREA
                         XIJICOMM-IN
                         XZUGOTMY-IN

      *@1.2 출력영역 확보
           #GETOUT       YPJLB274-CA

      *@1.3 COMMON AREA SETTING 공통IC프로그램 호출
      *    고객번호
           MOVE YNJLB274-KB-PIN        TO AACOM-CUST-IDNFR

           #DYCALL IJICOMM YCCOMMON-CA XIJICOMM-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과 확인
           IF COND-XIJICOMM-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XIJICOMM-R-ERRCD
                     XIJICOMM-R-TREAT-CD
                     XIJICOMM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
