      *    fld신청번호
           MOVE YNJLB274-APLCN-NO
             TO XDJLB274-I-APLCN-NO
      *    신청직원번호
           MOVE YNJLB274-APLCN-EMPID
             TO XDJLB274-I-APLCN-EMPID
      *    fld승인일자
           MOVE YNJLB274-ATHOR-YMD
             TO XDJLB274-I-ATHOR-YMD
      *    fld승인한도
           MOVE YNJLB274-LIMT-ATHOR-AMT
             TO XDJLB274-I-LIMT-ATHOR-AMT
220428*    한도승인권자구분
           MOVE YNJLB274-LIMT-ATRZ-DSTCD
             TO XDJLB274-I-LIMT-ATRZ-DSTCD
      *    fld승인유효기일
           MOVE YNJLB274-LIMT-STUP-VALD-YMD
             TO XDJLB274-I-LIMT-STUP-VALD-YMD
      *    cbo승인구분
           MOVE YNJLB274-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTCD
             TO XDJLB274-I-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTCD
      *    mln승인의견
           MOVE YNJLB274-ATHOR-RESN-CTNT
             TO XDJLB274-I-ATHOR-RESN-CTNT
231012*    한도신청종류구분
           MOVE YNJLB274-LIMT-A-KND-DSTCD
             TO XDJLB274-I-LIMT-A-KND-DSTCD

      *@3.1.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJLB274 YCCOMMON-CA XDJLB274-CA

      *@3.1.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@실행조건:COND-XDJLB274-OK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF COND-XDJLB274-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XDJLB274-R-ERRCD
                     XDJLB274-R-TREAT-CD
                     XDJLB274-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3100-DJLB274-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

